</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E6EDF3\"> {</span></span>\n    32\u2192<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#FF7B72\">  return</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#FF7B72\"> !</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E6EDF3\">data.draft;</span></span>\n    33\u2192<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E6EDF3\">});</span></span></code></pre>\n    34\u2192<p>This enables building dynamic, type-safe blogs with excellent developer experience.</p>  </div> <!-- Article Footer --> <footer class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pt-8\"> <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"> <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300\"> <p>Thanks for reading!</p> </div> <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4\"> <a href=\"/myblog\" class=\"inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-300 hover:text-primary-700 dark:hover:text-primary-200 transition-colors\">\n    35\u2192\u2190 Back to all posts\n    36\u2192</a> </div> </div> </footer> </article>  </main> <!-- Footer --> <footer class=\"border-t border-theme-border-primary bg-theme-bg-secondary theme-transition\"> <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-8\"> <div class=\"text-center text-sm text-theme-text-secondary\"> <p>&copy; 2025 Ali Alqattan. All rights reserved.</p> <p class=\"mt-2\">\n    37\u2192Built with <a href=\"https://astro.build\" class=\"theme-link\">Astro</a>\n    38\u2192and deployed on <a href=\"https://pages.github.com\" class=\"theme-link\">GitHub Pages</a> </p> </div> </div> </footer> </div> <!-- Mermaid theme integration --> <script type=\"module\" src=\"/myblog/_astro/MermaidTheme.astro_astro_type_script_index_0_lang.C58rMkyz.js\"></script>  </body></html>\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it looks malicious. If it does, you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can 